Median Filter with kernel size [3, 3]¶

In [3]:
selem = square(3)
for i in range(3):
    image[:, :, i] = median(image[:, :, i], selem)
plt.imshow(image.astype('uint8'))
Out[3]:
<matplotlib.image.AxesImage at 0x7f5c79956080>
